Interface IJavascriptObject

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BingMaps, Circle, Cluster, ClusterStyle, Coordinate, CoordinateProjected, DefaultGeoJsonLoader, Feature, Feature, Fill, GeoJson, GeoJsonFormat, Icon, Image, Interaction, JavascriptObject, Layer, Loader, LongLat, Map, Modify, Osm, Overlay, PersistentFeature, Point, Popover, PopoverOverlay, Projection, ServerVector, Source, StaticVector, Stroke, Style, Text, Tile, TileJson, TileWms, Vector, VectorSource, View

    public interface IJavascriptObject
    Provides an interface for all objects that render to Javascript.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getJsId()
      Returns a String with the unique ID used to identify this object.
      String getJsType()
      Returns a String with the type of Javascript object that this object represents.
      String renderJs()
      Returns a String with containing the rendered Javascript code for this object.
